HEADWORD: Dyslysin
<hw>Dys"ly*sin</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>dys-</grk> ill, hard + <?/ a loosing.]</ety> <fld>(Physiol.
